mixin header(data)
    include ScribCard.pug 
    div
        div(class="bg-orange-200 grid lg:grid-cols-2 2xl:grid-cols-5")
            div(class="px-8 py-12 max-w-md mx-auto sm:max-w-xl lg:px-12 lg:py-24 lg:max-w-full xl:mr-0 2xl:col-span-2")
                div(class="xl:max-w-xl")
                    img(class="h-10 w-96", src="/img/logo.svg", alt="Website icon")
                    img(class="mt-6 rounded-lg shadow-xl sm:mt-8 sm:w-full sm:object-cover object-center lg:hidden", src="/img/scrib.jpg", alt="A beautiful Scrib")

                    h1(class="mt-6 text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:mt-8 sm:text-4xl lg:text-3xl xl:text-4xl font-headline tracking-tight") You can find Scribs anywhere.
                        br(class="inline md:hidden")
                        span(class="text-orange-700") Watch out.
                    p(class="mt-1 text-grap-600 sm:mt-4 sm:text-xl") Scrib are like the natural predator of a newborn baby; at the start of the game, fighting one is a death sentence for you. If you can't reliably hit them they'll stunlock you, with a paralysis spell, so you should skip town to find someone who can train your primary weapon skill.
                    div(class="mt-4 sm:mt-6")
                        a(href="/balmora", class="btn btn-indigo mr-4") Go to Balmora
                        a(href="", class="btn btn-gray") I love scrib
            div(class="hidden relative lg:block 2xl:col-span-3")
                img(class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-center", src="../img/scrib.jpg", alt="A beautiful Scrib")

        div(class="max-w-md sm:max-w-xl lg:max-w-6xl mx-auto px-8 lg:px-12 py-8")
            h2(class="text-xl text-gray-900") Popular scrib
            p(class="mt-2 text-gray-600") A selection of friendly, non-blighted pedigree Scrib. Who needs a Guar with Scrib like these?
            div(class="mt-6 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3 active:bg-white-100")
                each [key,scrib] of data
                    +ScribCard(scrib)